1) Download Node js from Nodejs Website & Install it.

2) Check node.js version
  - open cmd & Enter "node -V"
  - npm -V

3) Install VS studio 

4) Create Node app package
  - open cmd & type "install -g create-react-app"

5) Create the app using create-react-app command (use this step for creating new project)
 - create new folder & open the folder -> select location and type "cmd" (automaticaly open cmp)
 - create-react-app myapp (wait for creating app)
 - cd myapp
 - npm start
 
